+ Use

This is the Cuban Ministry of Anomalies (CMA) Theme, a theme made by [[*user Dc_Yerko]] with indications from [[*user Uncle Nicolini]] for their use in article with a point of view of the ES' Group of Interest  "[http://scp-int.wikidot.com/mac-hub Cuban Ministry of Anomalies]".

To use this theme, put the following line in the top part of your article:

> @@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:mac]]@@

Revolutionary[[footnote]]Radical, collectivist even.[[/footnote]][[footnote]]Marxist-Leninist, others will say.[[/footnote]]

